9 An Act relating to professions and occupations;
amending 59 O.S. 2021, Section 15.8, as last amended
10 by Section 2, Chapter 192, O.S.L. 2025 (59 O.S. Supp.
2025, Section 15.8), which relates to qualifications
11 to take an examination for accounting; modifying
educational requirements; describing educational
12 course requirements; amending 59 O.S. 2021, Section
15.9, as last amended by Section 2, Chapter 192,
13 O.S.L. 2025 (59 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 15.9), which
relates to issuing accounting certificates; deleting
14 and modifying certain educational eligibility
requirements to align with Uniform Accountancy Act;
15 amending 59 O.S. 2021, Section 15.12A, as last
amended by Section 3, Chapter 26, O.S.L. 2023 (59
16 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 15.12A), which relates to
out-of-state licensed accounting business; deleting
17 equivalency provision; providing pathway for in-state
licensure; listing educational requirements; deleting
18 out-of-state certificate or license exemption;
amending 59 O.S. 2021, Section 15.13, as last amended
19 by Section 6, Chapter 26, O.S.L. 2025 (59 O.S. Supp.
2025, Section 15.13), which relates to public
20 accounting certificates; modifying required documents
for application; deleting and creating new conditions
21 for applicants that do not meet certain requirements;
and providing an effective date.
